article.description: — Kendric Davis had 20 points as SMU defeated Temple 79-68 on Monday.
article.headline: Davis scores 20 to carry SMU past Temple 79-68
article.linkText: Davis scores 20 to carry SMU past Temple 79-68
article.story: DALLAS -- — Kendric Davis had 20 points as SMU defeated Temple 79-68 on Monday. Feron Hunt had 18 points and nine rebounds for SMU (7-2, 3-2 American Athletic Conference). Emmanuel Bandoumel added 16 points and eight rebounds, and Ethan Chargois had 12 points and five assists. Brendan Barry had 17 points for the Owls (1-3, 0-3). Damian Dunn added 17 points, and J.P. Moorman II had eight rebounds. The Mustangs improve to 2-0 against the Owls this season. SMU defeated Temple 79-71 on Dec. 30. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
